b.23354-ref2012">2012</xref>]3125号)；贵州省卫生厅基金项目(NO: gzwkj 2012-1-023)。</p></sec><sec id="s8"><title>文章引用</title><p>王 蕾,彭吾训,龚 翔,王 健,张 祎,王 帅. 氟、砷联合对人成骨细胞活性及形态的交互作用The Interaction between Fluoride and Arsenic on the Activity and Morphology of Human Osteoblast[J]. 外科, 2018, 07(01): 1-8. http://dx.doi.org/10.12677/HJS.2018.71001</p></sec><sec id="s9"><title>参考文献 (References)</title></sec></body><back><ref-list><title>References</title><ref id="hanspub.23354-ref1"><label>1</label><mixed-citation publication-type="other" xlink:type="simple">Jadhav, S.V., Bringas, E., Yadav, G.D., et al. (2015) Arsenic and Fluoride Contaminated Groundwaters: A Review of Current Tech-nologies for Contaminants Removal. Journal of Environmental Management, 162, 306-325.</mixed-citation></ref><ref id="hanspub.23354-ref2"><label>2</label><mixed-citation publication-type="other" xlink:type="simple">Zeng, Q.B., Xu, Y.Y., Yu, X., et al. (2014) Arsenic May Be Involved in Fluoride-Induced Bone Toxicity through PTH/PKA/AP1 Signaling Pathway. Environmental Toxicology and Pharmacology, 37, 228-233.</mixed-citation></ref><ref id="hanspub.23354-ref3"><label>3</label><mixed-citation publication-type="other" xlink:type="simple">Pan, L.L., Shi, X.G., Liu, S., et al. (2014) Flouride Promotes Osteoblastic Dif-ferentiation through Canonical Wnt/β-Catenin Signaling Pathway. Toxicology Letters, 225, 34-42.</mixed-citation></ref><ref id="hanspub.23354-ref4"><label>4</label><mixed-citation publication-type="other" xlink:type="simple">Zhang, Y.L., Luo, Q., Deng, Q., et al. (2015) Genes Associated with Sodium Fluoride-Induced Human Osteoblast Apoptosis. International Journal of Clinical and Experimental Medicine, 8, 13171-13178.</mixed-citation></ref><ref id="hanspub.23354-ref5"><label>5</label><mixed-citation publication-type="other" xlink:type="simple">Hong, F., Zheng, C., Xu, D.G., et al. (2013) Chronic Combined Effects of Fluoride and Arsenite on the Runx2 and Downstream Related Factors of Bonemetabolism in Rats. 